      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'll look into the cycle counting. one thing though, we've double checked the scan logs and the physical handling seems pretty tight. we even checked the cameras for the high-value aisles. it's almost like they just... disappear. is there any other logical reason for small-scale loss if it isn't theft or scanning errors?",
