      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's possible, but our damage reports are actually pretty high, and these missing units don't seem to match up with any reported spoiled items. it's just these tiny gaps, like individual resistors or single MCUs missing here and there. it's super frustrating because it's so hard to pin down. do you think there's anything else that could cause \"ghost\" inventory issues like this?",
